DISCIPLINARY CASES

2010-0693. Cleveland Metro. Bar Assn. v. Johnson.

This cause is pending before the court upon the filing of a report of the Board of Commissioners on Grievances and Discipline recommending the court to impose discipline against the respondent. On June 18, 2010, respondent’s counsel filed a motion to withdraw as counsel. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by the court that the motion to withdraw as counsel is granted.
